  'install.faq1q': 'What is a PWA?',
  'install.faq1a': 'A Progressive Web App (PWA) is a web app that installs directly from your browser to your device. It works like a native app with full-screen mode, push notifications, and offline support — all without needing an app store.',
  'install.faq2q': 'Is it safe to install the APK?',
  'install.faq2a': 'Yes! Our APK is digitally signed with an official VEX certificate. You can verify the signature before installing. Just make sure you download it only from this official page.',
  'install.faq3q': 'Does the app work offline?',
